title: LA City Terrace Park Rail
content:
Consider the following skateboarding’s roll of honor:

Ryan Decenzo – Fs boardslide – ‘Double Down’
TJ Rogers – Switch boardslide – Blind ‘X2 Vision’
David Gonzalez – Feeble – ‘Possessed To Skate’
Ed Duff – Smithgrind – Zero ‘Cold War’
Chase Webb – Fs 5-0 – ‘The Flat Earth’
Chase Webb – Fs nosegrind – ‘Welcome to Pizza’
Justin Figueroa – Crooked – Emerica ‘Made Chapter 2’
Nyjah Huston – Bs 5-0 & kickflip bs 50-50 – Nike SB ‘Til Death’
